Hi guysI know you are all up in arms about this EBAY seller.I=
&#39;d like to say something from the view from someone new to this interest.I =
for one have been desperate for answers. I lost my mom almost a year ago an=
d have been searching desperately for an answer (do we go somewhere ? can w=
e still talk to each other somehow ?) This goes on to a point most of you w=
ould think is pathetic.I have contacted many of you offline for help, to pu=
rchase or just to ask for help on making a device myself with limited elect=
ronic knowledge. All of you have been helpful or at least responded to an e=
mail. So, I went with one suggestion, I hacked a 20-125. I have to say, I a=
m quite disappointed. I have tried whole heartedly to sit and listen and wa=
it in many sessions as you call them. If anyone could get the thing to work=
 out of pure desperation, it is myself !!!of course my main goal was to rea=
ch my mother, but at this point any spirit would do, just to hear something=
 in response to my questions. I had nothing in return.I have a good ear to =
listen for any response, it is not as simple as not hearing properly. In fa=
ct I seem to have capture one voice with my recorder alone in the beginning=
, but nothing since.There is a frustration in reading posts from most those=
 that seem to continuously build these things that can work and actually co=
mmunicate.To be honest, I think this person is taking a great leap and a gr=
eat risk in offering these devices out to the public. If people purchase th=
em with great hopes like myself of speaking to a deceased loved one and not=
hing comes through. This guys reputation in mush on EBAY.I for one am at a =
frustration point ready to give up. I tried to be a part of all of you, wit=
h something to contribute, a voice , a response or something. I almost feel=
 like crying.The only weird thing is the radio will turn itself on. I have =
pulled the batteries out of it because it&#39;s annoying. A good 40.00 gone to =
nothing in such desperation !!! If someone wants to test this box or to see=
 if it works I&#39;d appreciate it. Holly  






